        <title>description of components of projectile motion</title>
        <contents>&lt;p&gt;As you have just seen in the videos, projectile motion can be analyzed in terms of the horizontal, x, and vertical, y, components of its motion. The x and y motions are best described as:&lt;/p&gt;</contents>
        <contentsformat>1</contentsformat>
